    <data key="d0">Arc Publishing Web Rendering Platform</data>
    <data key="d1">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0JxJpNjI9Y0</data>
    <data key="d2">Highly available multi-tier rendering architecture supporting 5-10% dynamic cache misses, leveraging ElastiCache for raw content API cache and S3 for pre-rendered pages.</data>
